506
00:28:27,737 --> 00:28:30,667
You're not fine.

507
00:28:30,695 --> 00:28:32,605
Look around you.

508
00:28:32,627 --> 00:28:35,847
Do you have any idea how
much trouble you're in?

509
00:28:39,015 --> 00:28:40,335
mom!

510
00:28:41,581 --> 00:28:42,331
Mom!

511
00:28:42,346 --> 00:28:44,236
Henry

512
00:28:46,823 --> 00:28:49,323
Henry, wait.

513
00:28:58,403 --> 00:29:00,563
I warned you to leave them alone.

514
00:29:00,586 --> 00:29:03,426
I couldn't, because you did.

515
00:29:03,453 --> 00:29:06,063
Look, i didn't know that you were
sick, and i'm sorry that you died,

516
00:29:06,099 --> 00:29:08,069
But you have to move on,
you have to let them go.

517
00:29:08,091 --> 00:29:10,321
Go? Go where?

518
00:29:10,365 --> 00:29:12,935
Do you have any idea
what you're talking about?

519
00:29:12,961 --> 00:29:14,931
There are people who
will take care of them.

520
00:29:14,953 --> 00:29:16,993
The county, you mean.

521
00:29:17,016 --> 00:29:19,036
Didn't you have any
relatives? Did your husband?

522
00:29:19,058 --> 00:29:20,468
There's no one.

523
00:29:20,487 --> 00:29:22,257
Well, what about friends?

524
00:29:22,277 --> 00:29:25,577
I mean, you went through the
trouble of doing all this planning.

525
00:29:25,608 --> 00:29:28,648
