534
00:30:02,803 --> 00:30:05,233
I couldn't tell you, i just couldn't.

535
00:30:05,258 --> 00:30:07,418
Ned: no, i feel bad.

536
00:30:07,441 --> 00:30:12,491
If i hadn't pushed to get closer, maybe
you guys could have just gone alone.

537
00:30:14,152 --> 00:30:18,182
