if i didn't like you so much.

538
00:30:18,216 --> 00:30:20,356
I do, ned.

539
00:30:20,389 --> 00:30:23,049
You hear me, right?

540
00:30:24,021 --> 00:30:26,671
Yeah. I hear you.

541
00:30:35,159 --> 00:30:38,019
I have to go.

542
00:30:38,771 --> 00:30:41,701
Can i see you tomorrow?

543
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:46,410
I'd love that.

544
00:30:52,484 --> 00:30:54,364
You kids are incredible.

545
00:30:54,385 --> 00:30:57,085
You didn't let me cook,
at least let me clean up.

546
00:30:57,112 --> 00:30:58,852
We have an alternating chore list.

547
00:30:58,872 --> 00:31:00,072
