00:33:20,893 --> 00:33:25,913
Because if you think you're gonna end up with a
nice family with lisa tucking you in every night,

590
00:33:25,953 --> 00:33:28,053
- You're not.
- Shut up.

591
00:33:29,052 --> 00:33:30,512
Look...

592
00:33:30,823 --> 00:33:33,773
I'm almost 18, but you guys...

