this is what mom told us to do.

596
00:33:44,737 --> 00:33:48,927
We have to stick together,
we have to be tough.

597
00:33:49,566 --> 00:33:51,296
Ok.

598
00:33:51,317 --> 00:33:53,417
We have to go.

