Henry? Henry?Henry!

600
00:33:57,062 --> 00:33:58,832
Where'd he go?

601
00:33:58,853 --> 00:34:01,763
Henry? Henry?

602
00:34:06,288 --> 00:34:09,058
Henry: sorry, you guys.

603
00:34:09,085 --> 00:34:12,945
But i just can't do this anymore.

604
