00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:07,810
Deserve a second chance?

675
00:38:12,610 --> 00:38:15,200
You all do.

676
00:38:20,497 --> 00:38:21,237
What are you doing?

677
00:38:21,252 --> 00:38:22,842
Oh, i'm just picking up ned.

678
00:38:22,862 --> 00:38:26,572
He wanted to help lisa's aunt
move the rest of her  tuff in.

679
00:38:27,148 --> 00:38:27,898
Are you guys ok?

680
00:38:27,912 --> 00:38:30,772
I mean, did he ever apologize
for just walking out?

681
