give them their privacy.

688
00:38:52,380 --> 00:38:55,750
This is me... Letting go.

689
00:38:56,666 --> 00:38:58,986
So what are they
doing? Are they kissing?

690
00:38:59,011 --> 00:39:00,601
Uh, no, she just hit him.

