00:39:24,193 --> 00:39:26,823
- Yeah.
- Ok, now mom.

702
00:39:26,849 --> 00:39:29,939
I rember mom taking
henry to work one day.

703
00:39:29,968 --> 00:39:31,698
i love this one.

