00:40:20,726 --> 00:40:24,496
I remember making up a
game with your mother.

716
00:40:25,686 --> 00:40:28,046
It was called "i rember."

717
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:30,050
Sweetheart, listen.

718
00:40:30,072 --> 00:40:32,942
'Cause after our parents died,

